Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:18.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状況は非科学的に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情のモンタージュ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}誰が誰を呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:30.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向けば　逃げてく視線　感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:33.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気のせいじゃつれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.49,0:24:38.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}アンテナは才能って言うでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:42.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}だってだって　知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:44.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は違うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.25,0:24:50.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}青春の温度差　今のうち　正してあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:55.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}明日解決するなら　今でもよくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.51,0:25:01.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君のミステリー　解いてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.22,0:25:05.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}少年の秘密めいた背中探せ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.94,0:25:09.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今日も君はファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.57,0:25:13.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惹けれてゆくよ　ずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.32,0:25:19.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨らんだ好奇心　トリックはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:23.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気になるよ　興味深い
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.46,0:25:25.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:18.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状况完全不科学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情如拼贴画般交织
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是谁在将谁呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:30.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}回头时感觉到你逃避的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:33.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}说这是错觉未免无情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.49,0:24:38.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}直觉该称为才能才对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:42.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:44.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}难道你并非如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.25,0:24:50.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在就为你纠正青春的温差
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:55.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}既然明天能解决 不如趁现在搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.51,0:25:01.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我想要解开你的悬疑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.22,0:25:05.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}探寻少年神秘的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.94,0:25:09.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天的你也如同幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.57,0:25:13.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狡猾地吸引着我不断沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.32,0:25:19.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨胀的好奇中分明不含心机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:23.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人在意 耐人寻味
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.46,0:25:25.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}这究竟是为什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没找到吗 那本「傍晚便成骸」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是暑假的时候带回乡下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.66,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：摩耶花COS的是赤冢不二夫「甜蜜小天使」中的主角加贺美厚子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.49,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：河内COS的是KOF系列的金
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那你就帮着画海报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海报…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 要萌的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐…把漫画的名字记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:24.66,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\blur3\pos(1212,880)}Wild Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同学 摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了料理竞赛是十一点半开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得在漫研画海报才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那么把摩耶花排在最后出场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你十二点十分到就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我会想办法的 那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我也得到总务委员会去露个脸才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他倒是很享受KANYA祭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个搬到体育馆去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 学长你不去到处逛逛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做的杂事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是都稍微看过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么有趣的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 听说围棋部出现了怪盗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷走了棋子 还留下了犯罪声明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是吗 围棋部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 不过我觉得只是部员自导自演而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我听冈野说无伴奏合唱部也出了类似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 冷饮箱里的一瓶饮料被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有犯罪声明？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说里面装着一张奇怪的便条
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下可好玩起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 福部 笑嘻嘻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我一定会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等卖出去了再谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 定价和数量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一本200日元 数量有…200本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下错订单所以印多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想尽量多卖一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降到150日元 给我20本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们的小册子一起以200元的价格捆绑销售
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是做什么 给我一本样书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我没带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后带上实物去找人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换一个求助方式 效果就会大有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入须学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入须学姐很擅长拜托别人做事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请教我一招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论要拜托什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要引导对方主动行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 就必须让对方身心都感到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体方法有很多 不过你能用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是让对方觉得他肩负着你的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让对方觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能做到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后对方就很容易竭尽全力来帮你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竭尽全力来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也不要把问题说得太严重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说得太严重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让对方觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他而言只是举手之劳的事 对你而言却很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是在没人的地方 找异性帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把文集拿来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢赐教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trick or Treat？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.79,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：孩子们在万圣节讨要点心时必说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trick or Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点心研究会的访问销售
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来袋饼干怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一袋100日元哟 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着这个去卖东西好像不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用两袋饼干跟你们换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在买文集附送那把手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再送你这个 当作南瓜给你的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面粉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trick or Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz274.477\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs45\c&H718886&\3c&HDBEAEB&\b1\pos(873,204)}超速度!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz274.477\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs45\c&H718886&\3c&HDBEAEB&\b1\pos(786,348)}海报绘制大比拼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz274.477\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs45\c&H718886&\3c&HDBEAEB&\b1\pos(708,528)}漫画研究会引以为傲的画手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz274.477\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs45\c&H718886&\3c&HDBEAEB&\b1\pos(589.5,517.5)}魔女VS女豹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫画研究会引以为傲的画手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还在忙着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信摩耶花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 福部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们队的须原
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是酒家的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那还挺厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就好好加油吧 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「好好」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 本次众所瞩目的参赛队伍有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一队 好滋味队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二队 摩根勒菲队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.10,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：Fata Morgana 亚瑟王传奇中登场的女巫 也有海市蜃楼的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三队 天文部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及四队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各队以三人为一组 每人限时20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20分过后换下一位队员上场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一人做菜时其他人不得插嘴 否则视为犯规
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同学打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做福部流海鲜炒饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米饭得从淘米蒸饭做起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 福部同学就要做压轴的大将了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然做不了海鲜炒饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第几个出场都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各队每人做一道菜以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食材在中央的台子上 先下手为强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果食材用完了 允许从校内补充
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 打头阵的选手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Own your kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs52.5}请各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wild
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fire！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.00,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(1100,178)\blur2}秋 分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.00,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,342)\blur2}昼夜等长日 乃是秋分时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 Wild Fire料理竞赛开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各队将会为我们带来什么样的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 古典部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在将鱼干的头部和内脏一一摘除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是精细的手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 你觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先处理是很重要的 副部长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根勒菲队准备了蛤仔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要做白萝卜酱汤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 福部同学 那样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没削萝卜皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提示是犯规的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮 皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 要一块块削吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水在沸腾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队 这样好像要花很多时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在莫比乌斯环之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.69,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：出自「机动战士高达 逆袭的夏亚」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各队要做什么现在还不明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 古典部队好像犯难了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是肉汤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 好滋味队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是经典中的经典 肉酱汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照这个速度会赶不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先锋选手们 时间就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Change Element
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs52.5}换  人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.48,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：出自「创圣的大天使」 其中的Vector Machine可更换驾驶员(即Change Element)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 只做了一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 千反田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太惊人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队主力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常精彩的刀工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是白萝卜的真正姿态 太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为是皮 现在污染的河流好像都要被净化了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:37.42,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：「河」与「皮」在日语中同音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了 已经做好一道菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然要有千反田同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 古典部居然用拜神式淘米法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且毫不可惜地把仅有6升的水倒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为米的美味下了必死的决心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 天文部队主力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊 是什么料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过激fire
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.07,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：「超时空要塞7」中热气·巴萨拉常说的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面 古典部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是拟似豆腐烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.66,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：豆腐捣碎加各种材料使其看上去像是蛋或其他菜的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故乡的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裕美！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.54,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：杉田智和的朋友的妈妈的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拟似豆腐烧什么的听都没听过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 摩根勒菲队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照烧鰤鱼正渐入佳境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Brilliant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs52.5}太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.34,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：「女神异闻录3」中桐条美鹤常说的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部的拟似豆腐烧做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着肚子都饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位主力究竟是何许人也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪农地主千反田家长女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田爱琉大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来看看天文部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的前卫派料理还在进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑暗吞噬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.40,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：杉田智和在「苍翼默示录」中所配角色的招式之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把煮好的土豆和片栗粉一起放进了研钵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要做薯饼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部很熟练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这下子不妙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙？什么不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队 提示是犯规的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 她没理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此已经过去了40分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请换大将上场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同学 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厉害啊 千反田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道你这么会做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 了不起了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有食材了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 终于进入大将战了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好滋味队准备了苹果作为甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐地雕出兔子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部的大将还没出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 好滋味队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了兔子之外 还开始雕花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好滋味队无视大将还没现身的古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备起甜点来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！赛场跑进了一个穿便装的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是古典部队的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来得及吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队的大将 终于登场了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 古典部队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一波方平一波又起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食材已经用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果什么都做不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大将战自然只能得鸭蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路奋战到现在的古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能止步于此了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队 拿下了小号洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是靠这么个小洋葱能做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大将似乎没有主意 只是站在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢 古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一道菜也做不出来的话可是要出局的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算拿那么点食材怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都要怪谁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部大将 束手无策！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.70,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：「夜航」 安托万·德·圣-埃克絮佩里出版于1931年的小说 法国著名文学奖费米娜奖获奖作品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完工了 摩根勒菲队的蛋包饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想 快想想！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队要在此倒下了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该 应该能做些什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队 无计可施！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的时间只有十分钟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能就此等待时间用尽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:54.78,UP_Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同学 刚才是不是有人叫你？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:01.95,UP_Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:05.37,UP_Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文部队 把香蕉用来煮酱汁了！香…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.38,UP_Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活动室那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志 过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到正下面来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作快！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队 先锋回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！意想不到的超展开！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那难道是面粉吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有违反规则 那就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.45,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：后半句原出自「苍天航路」中曹操的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下七分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wild Fire料理竞赛 各队进入收尾阶段时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队终于行动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这极端不利的环境下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们究竟会如何奋战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们竟然把甜虾的头取出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鲜什锦炸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海鲜什锦炸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wild Fire料理竞赛 倒计时五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 料理研 至少也要准备好圆勺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圆勺 圆勺 对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了圆勺的古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于开始进行下一步工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 古典部队 正以怒涛之势展开反击！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海鲜什锦炸盖饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队 他们来得及吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一分钟！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捞起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往上放萝卜丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 现在宣布结果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获胜的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部队！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没炸透
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间不够又别无选择的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到这样已经很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有圆勺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有圆勺就能做得很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿那个居然花了一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也够笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然没有就该想没有的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 实在非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明明认真确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该最后再检查一遍的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也一开始就觉得奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我应该确认的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先离开一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪声明…！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:59.45,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\blur3\fs48\pos(722,885)}欢迎来到KANYA祭！
